<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/user/user_service/style_about.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  <% if (user && user.role === 'S') { %>
    <%- include('../../partials/user_partials/nav_senior') %>
  <% } else { %>
    <%- include('../../partials/user_partials/nav_about') %>
  <% } %>

  <main class="nopill-main">
    <div class="nopill-card">

      <div class="nopill-icon">
        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M10 7V5a2 2 0 014 0v2"/>
          <path d="M12 12v4M10 14h4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="nopill-card__title">약통 등록</h1>
      <p class="nopill-card__desc">
        스마트 약상자 하단의 시리얼 번호를 입력해 주세요.<br>
        등록 후 바로 대시보드를 이용하실 수 있습니다.
      </p>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <p class="login-error" style="color: #dc2626; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><%= error %></p>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/user/senior_info/senior_register-pillbox" method="POST" class="pillbox-form">
        
        <div class="pillbox-form__group">
          <label for="pillboxId">약통 시리얼 번호</label>
          
        <input
            type="text"
            id="pillboxNum"
            name="pillboxNum"
            placeholder="예: PB-2025-XXXX"
            required>
          <span class="pillbox-form__hint">약상자 하단 스티커에서 확인하실 수 있습니다.</span>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">등록하기</button>
      </form>

      <div class="nopill-links" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/user/user_service/medicine_buy" class="nopill-card__link" style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7a9a; text-decoration: none;">
          약통이 없으신가요? 구매하러 가기 →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2025 복약안심서비스 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Team Jetson5 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 스마트 약상자 기반 복약 관리 플랫폼</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>